---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="History - Anno 1728" lang="en">
	<div class="page-header">
		<h1>History of the House</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">Nearly 300 years of architectural history to experience</p>
	</div>

	<div class="intro-box">
		<p>
			The vacation home is a heritage-protected half-timbered house in Wiesbaden-Auringen,
			built around <strong>1728</strong>. When acquired, it was a ruin on the verge of collapse,
			but was elaborately <strong>restored rather than merely renovated</strong>.
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="details-section">
		<h2>Architectural Features</h2>

		<div class="detail-card">
			<div class="detail-icon">üèõÔ∏è</div>
			<div class="detail-content">
				<h3>Architecture</h3>
				<p>
					The house is crooked and tilted. Especially on the first floor, you may experience
					a feeling of "sea motion." This is intentional and typical of the Baroque period.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="detail-card">
			<div class="detail-icon">ü™ú</div>
			<div class="detail-content">
				<h3>The Staircase</h3>
				<p>
					The staircase resembles a fixed ladder more than a modern staircase with flat steps.
					Historically, people descended the staircase backwards, which is why the steps are "foot-deep" ‚Äì
					this direction of movement is recommended.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="detail-card">
			<div class="detail-icon">ü™µ</div>
			<div class="detail-content">
				<h3>Wooden Floors</h3>
				<div class="floor-info">
					<div class="floor-item">
						<span class="floor-label">Living Room</span>
						<span class="floor-value">Floorboards from the 1920s</span>
					</div>
					<div class="floor-item">
						<span class="floor-label">Staircase & 1st Floor</span>
						<span class="floor-value">Original from ca. 1728</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="floor-note">All floors were elaborately restored, supplemented, and oiled.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="detail-card">
			<div class="detail-icon">ü™ü</div>
			<div class="detail-content">
				<h3>Windows</h3>
				<p>
					The oldest window in the first-floor hallway is older than the house itself ‚Äì
					already in 1728, used windows were recycled. The new windows were crafted
					after historical models with single glazing made of "antique glass."
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="detail-card">
			<div class="detail-icon">üé®</div>
			<div class="detail-content">
				<h3>Ceiling (Living Room)</h3>
				<p>
					The restoration was supported by the Hessian State Heritage Office.
					Original colored border strips were uncovered and preserved.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="cta-box">
		<p>Experience history for yourself!</p>
		<div class="cta-buttons">
			<a href="/en/vorderhaus/" class="button primary">To the Main House</a>
			<a href="/en/buchungen/" class="button secondary">Book now</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		color: #333;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.subtitle {
		color: #666;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.intro-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a5568 0%, #2d3748 100%);
		color: #fff;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.intro-box p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		color: #333;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.details-section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.detail-card {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		background: #fff;
		border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
		border-radius: 10px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
	}

	.detail-card:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
	}

	.detail-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		background: #f8f9fa;
		border-radius: 10px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.detail-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #333;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.detail-content p {
		margin: 0;
		color: #555;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.floor-info {
		background: #f8f9fa;
		border-radius: 8px;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.floor-item {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
	}

	.floor-item:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.floor-label {
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.floor-value {
		color: #333;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.floor-note {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #888;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.cta-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B2332 0%, #6B1A26 100%);
		color: #fff;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-box p {
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		transition: transform 0.2s;
	}

	.button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.button.primary {
		background: #8B2332;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.button.secondary {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
		color: #fff;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
	}

	.button.secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.detail-card {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.detail-icon {
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}
</style>
